flowchart TD
    Start([Mulai])
    OpenDashboard[Admin membuka dashboard]
    RoleCheck{Role admin?}
    Denied[Arahkan ke halaman utama]
    CountStats[Hitung total users events bookings favorites]
    CountStatus[Hitung booking pending approved rejected]
    LoadBookings[Ambil data booking join users dan events]
    LoadEvents[Ambil semua event join organizer]
    BuildChart[Susun label dan total chart booking per event]
    ShowDashboard[Tampilkan dashboard admin]
    End([Selesai])

    Start --> OpenDashboard --> RoleCheck
    RoleCheck -- Tidak --> Denied --> End
    RoleCheck -- Ya --> CountStats --> CountStatus --> LoadBookings --> LoadEvents --> BuildChart --> ShowDashboard --> End
